categories: Category:Battles of the Great Jedi Purge

nodes.text: During the early stages of the Great Jedi Purge in 19 BBY, Jedi Padawan Caleb Dume answered the Jedi beacon distress signal and attempted to return to the Jedi Temple on the planet Coruscant. However, he was ambushed by a number of Galactic Empire-owned Aggressive ReConnaissance-170 starfighters.
